# Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock IS checked in: the workspace produces binary artefacts
# (melete-app + the two wasm cdylibs consumed by the Amplify Hosting
# build), so reproducible builds need a pinned resolver state. Without
# this, CI / Amplify pulls the latest 0.2.x of wasm-bindgen on every
# run and breaks when the cli pin no longer matches the schema.

